            </imageobject>
            <imageobject role="html">
                <imagedata fileref="../shared/images/architecture.jpg" format="JPG" align="center"/>
            </imageobject>
        </mediaobject>

        <para>
            上图展示了所有APL UI组件的继承关系.
        </para>
    </sect1>

